definition.value: A polyprenyl phospho oligosaccharide where N-acetyl-beta-D-mannosaminyl-(1->4)-N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl comprises the oligosaccharide component and the polyprenyl chain consists of eleven prenyl units.
A 3-oxo-5beta-steroid that is 5beta-cholestane substituted by an oxo group at position 3.
A 11alpha-hydroxy steroid that is pregn-4-ene-3,20-dione substituted by a hydroxy group at position 11.
A D-glucose monophosphate in which the phosphate group is located at position 1.
